snippet.title: Zorro gameplay (PC Game, 1995)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Zorro, Dos PC game produced by Capstone in 1995 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/zorro/1164/
Playing the first stage of this quite difficutl platformer. You'll be zorro.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
